#: ../../../reference/images.md:58
msgid "Different images for dark/light mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/images.md:60
msgid ""
"Furo supports [light mode and dark mode](../customisation/colors) colours "
"out-of-the-box. However, certain images do not work well against certain "
"backgrounds (eg: if the image has a white background)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/images.md:64
msgid ""
"You can use the `only-light` and `only-dark` classes, to show different "
"images based on the currently active colour scheme."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/images.md:70
msgid ""
